c: 3
v: 28
t: "ynha allah almuminin 'an yatakhidhuu alkafirin 'awlia' balmhbt walnsrt min dun almwmnyn, wman yatawalahum faqad bri min allh, wallah bri' mnh, 'iilaa 'an takunuu deafana khayifin faqad rkhkhas allah lakum fi mhadnthm atqa' lshrhm, hataa taqwaa shwktkm, wayuhadhirukum allah nfsh, fatqwh wkhafwh. wa'iilaa allah wahdah rjwe alkhlayq llhsab waljza'"